---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";

const friends = [
  "https://mylyn.cn",
  "https://Kendal-ming.github.io",
  "http://blog.zerohzzzz.top",
  "https://unclezhou.top",
  "https://herveyb3b4.github.io",
  "https://salt114514.github.io/"
];
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`Links | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <style>
      ul {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 2rem 0 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      li a {
        display: block;
        padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: white;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(var(--black), 5%);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      small {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 0.25rem;
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Friend Links</h1>
      <p>原博客里的友链已经迁到这里，页面结构保持简单，后面继续加也不容易乱。</p>
      <ul>
        {
          friends.map((href) => (
            <li>
              <a href={href} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                {new URL(href).hostname.replace(/^www\./, "")}
                <small>{href}</small>
              </a>
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
